<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q42_v7" title="Q42_v7" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>En un teatro se instala una tarima rectangular para un escenario. Se sabe que la suma de las medidas de su largo y su ancho es de 
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>26</m:mn><m:mi>m</m:mi>
      </m:math>
      y que el área de la superficie de la tarima es de 
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>120</m:mn><m:msup><m:mi>m</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup>
      </m:math>.
      ¿Cuál es la medida del largo de la tarima?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>Selecciona una opción.</qti-prompt>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mi>m</m:mi>
        </m:math>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mi>m</m:mi>
        </m:math>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mi>m</m:mi>
        </m:math>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>26</m:mn><m:mi>m</m:mi>
        </m:math>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
  </qti-item-body>
<qti-response-processing template="https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml" /></qti-assessment-item>